## Features

### System Tray:
- Status indicator icons (connected, disconnected, error, connecting)
- Menu: Show/Hide, New Tab, Recent Connections (5), Settings, Background Mode, Run at Startup, Quit
- Left-click: show/hide window
- Right-click: context menu
- Double-click: open main window maximized
- Tooltip with active sessions count
- Minimize to tray on close
- Start minimized option
- Run at startup option
- Background mode: keep connections alive saat window closed

### Notifications:
- Native notifications: macOS Notification Center, Windows Toast, Linux Notify
- Notification types: connection status, transfer complete, transfer progress, security alert, session recording, update available, system message, error, info, success
- Actions: open, dismiss, mute, acknowledge, reconnect, view details
- History: notification log with 100 entries max, 30 days retention
- Rate limiting: 5 second interval per type
- Do Not Disturb mode
- Per-type preferences
- Unread count badge
- Platform-specific sound configuration

### Integration:
- Auto-sandbox on session create
- Graceful degradation (log warning, continue)
- Prometheus metrics + alerts
- Tauri state management
- Frontend event emission
